text: Cell Systems is a bimonthly peer-reviewed scientific journal covering research in systems biology. The journal was established in 2015 and published by Cell Press. According to the Journal Citation Reports, the journal has a 2018 impact factor of 8.673. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Biology journals Category:English-language journals Category:Cell Press academic journals Category:Publications established in 2015 Category:Bimonthly journals
